OL,3,CTrial date set for Woman accused of
OL,4,Cshooting her partner to death with air
OL,5,Crifle
OL,7,FA woman is set to stand trial charged
OL,8,Fwith shooting her partner to death.
OL,10,FSimone Ramage is accused of
OL,11,Fdischarging an air rifle at Brian
OL,12,FKowbel, 40, at their home in
OL,13,FGalashiels on 17 February 2023.
OL,15,FThe allegation claims the 39 year-old
OL,16,Fshot him leaving him so severely hurt
OL,17,Fthat he later passed away in hospital.
