OL,7,FRamage faces three further charges
OL,8,Fincluding attempting to pervert the
OL,9,Fcourse of justice by concealing the
OL,10,Fair rifle under a sofa at the property.
OL,12,FShe was also charged with posession of
OL,13,Fan air rifle and "culpably and
OL,14,Frecklessly" firing the weapon towards
OL,15,Fa fence bordering a car park.
OL,17,FRamage's lawyer Mark Stewart, entered
OL,18,Fnot guilty pleas to her charges at the
OL,19,FHigh Court in Glasgow.
