OL,7,FThe KC said the case involved a
OL,8,F"slightly unusual subject matter".
OL,10,FMr Stewart: "The position is that the
OL,11,Faccused is someone who suffers greatly
OL,12,Ffrom as a consequence of the events."
OL,14,FHe added this had caused difficulty
OL,15,Ffor Ramage's lawyers in their
OL,16,Fpreparation of the case.
OL,18,FHowever, the defence advocate and
OL,19,Fprosecutor Erin Campbell each said
OL,20,Fthey were ready for a trial to be
OL,21,Ffixed.
